sequenceDiagram
  participant U as User
  participant API as Query/Chat API
  participant PERM as require_permission
  participant ACL as document_access filter
  participant IDX as Search/Index

  U->>API: Ask question
  API->>PERM: Evaluate effective permissions
  alt Denied
    PERM-->>API: Deny
    API-->>U: Fail-closed denial
  else Allowed
    PERM-->>API: Allow
    API->>ACL: Apply document ACL filters
    ACL->>IDX: Execute filtered retrieval
    IDX-->>API: Authorized chunks
    API-->>U: Response with permitted context
  end

  Note over ACL,IDX: Unknown: full coverage across all alternate retrieval surfaces
